#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_canvasitem.rst:21
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Base class of anything 2D. Canvas items are laid out in a tree; children "
"inherit and extend their parent's transform. ``CanvasItem`` is extended "
"by :ref:`Control <class_Control>` for anything GUI-related, and by "
":ref:`Node2D <class_Node2D>` for anything related to the 2D engine."
msgstr ""
"任何2D的基类。画布项目放置在一棵树上；子级继承并扩展了父级的变换。CanvasItem由 :ref:`Control "
"<class_Control>` 扩展为与GUI相关的任何内容，由 :ref:`Node2D <class_Node2D>` "
"扩展为与2D引擎相关的任何内容。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_canvasitem.rst:23
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Any ``CanvasItem`` can draw. For this, :ref:`update "
"<class_CanvasItem_method_update>` must be called, then "
":ref:`NOTIFICATION_DRAW <class_CanvasItem_constant_NOTIFICATION_DRAW>` "
"will be received on idle time to request redraw. Because of this, canvas "
"items don't need to be redrawn on every frame, improving the performance "
"significantly. Several functions for drawing on the ``CanvasItem`` are "
"provided (see ``draw_*`` functions). However, they can only be used "
"inside the :ref:`Object._notification "
"<class_Object_method__notification>`, signal or :ref:`_draw "
"<class_CanvasItem_method__draw>` virtual functions."
msgstr ""
"任何 ``CanvasItem`` 都可以绘制。为此，须调用 :ref:`update "
"<class_CanvasItem_method_update>`，然后在空闲时接收 :ref:`NOTIFICATION_DRAW "
"<class_CanvasItem_constant_NOTIFICATION_DRAW>`，以请求重绘。因此，不需要在每一帧上重新绘制画布项目，从而显著提高了性能。提供了一些在"
" ``CanvasItem`` 上进行绘制的函数（参见 ``draw_*`` 函数）。但是，它们只能在 "
":ref:`Object._notification <class_Object_method__notification>`、信号、或 "
":ref:`_draw <class_CanvasItem_method__draw>` 虚函数内部使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_canvasitem.rst:25
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Canvas items are drawn in tree order. By default, children are on top of "
"their parents so a root ``CanvasItem`` will be drawn behind everything. "
"This behavior can be changed on a per-item basis."
msgstr ""
"画布项目以树的顺序绘制。默认情况下，子级位于父级之上，因此一个根 ``CanvasItem`` "
"将被绘制在所有对象后面。这种行为可以在每个项目的基础上改变。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_canvasitem.rst:27
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A ``CanvasItem`` can also be hidden, which will also hide its children. "
"It provides many ways to change parameters such as modulation (for itself"
" and its children) and self modulation (only for itself), as well as its "
"blend mode."
msgstr ""
"一个 ``CanvasItem`` "
"也可以被隐藏，这也将隐藏其子级。它提供了许多更改参数的方式，例如调制（针对其自身及其子级）和自调制（仅针对自身），以及其混合模式。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_canvasitem.rst:29
msgid ""
"Ultimately, a transform notification can be requested, which will notify "
"the node that its global position changed in case the parent tree "
"changed."
msgstr "最终，可以请求一个变换通知，以在父级树发生更改的情况下，将通知节点，其全局位置已更改。"

